{
  "page": "Freedmen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg/350px-T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg/525px-T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg/700px-T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_liberated_slaves.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Liberated men in <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>, by Tomasz Jedruszek © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Freedmen</b> are people who have been freed from <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Freedmen are not allowed within the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Walls\" title=\"Black Walls\">Black Walls</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> unless invited by its denizens.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> frees the <a href=\"/index.php/Slaves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slaves\">slaves</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Astapor\" title=\"Fall of Astapor\">Astapor</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> with thousands of them following her north during her <a href=\"/index.php/Targaryen_campaign_in_Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Targaryen campaign in Slaver&#39;s Bay\">campaign in Slaver's Bay</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Thousands more former slaves join her host after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_near_Yunkai\" title=\"Battle near Yunkai\">battle near Yunkai</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> organizes the fighting men into four companies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Freedmen aid in Daenerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Siege of Meereen\">siege of Meereen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and half of the city's fighting slaves rise in rebellion against the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Half of Daenerys's freedmen are from <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Sons_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Sons of the Harpy\">Sons of the Harpy</a> attack unarmed freedmen <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> so Daenerys orders the creation of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brazen_Beasts\" title=\"Brazen Beasts\">Brazen Beasts</a>, a new city watch composed of <a href=\"/index.php/Shavepates\" title=\"Shavepates\">shavepates</a> and freedmen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> She also has <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Worm\" title=\"Grey Worm\">Grey Worm</a> turn companies of freedmen into soldiers, including the <a href=\"/index.php/Stalwart_Shields\" title=\"Stalwart Shields\">Stalwart Shields</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Brothers\" title=\"Free Brothers\">Free Brothers</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mother%27s_Men\" title=\"Mother&#39;s Men\">Mother's Men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_flux\" title=\"Bloody flux\">bloody flux</a> spreads among the freedmen at Meereen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The four mates of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Selaesori_Qhoran\" title=\"Selaesori Qhoran\">Selaesori Qhoran</a></i> are all freedmen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I told them they were free. I cannot tell them now they are not free to join me.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jorah</b>: The <a href=\"/index.php/Slaves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slaves\">slaves</a> are weak from the march.<br />\n</p><p><b>Daenerys</b>: Freedmen. They are slaves no longer.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Jorah</b>: Slave or free, they are hungry and they'll soon be sick.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Her children were the freedmen. <a href=\"/index.php/Mhysa\" title=\"Mhysa\">Mhysa</a>, they called her, all those whose chains she broke.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Freedmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, The Merchant's Man.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 43\">Chapter 43</a>, Daenerys VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 55\">Chapter 55</a>, The Queensguard.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403120139\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.068 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1610/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9268/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6595/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1004/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6562/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   49.570      1 -total\n 85.19%   42.229     16 Template:Ref\n 56.98%   28.246     16 Template:Ref/core\n 13.58%    6.731      3 Template:Quote\n  9.57%    4.742      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7791-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403120138 and revision id 293202\n -->\n",
